            Java(TM) 2 Runtime Environment, Standard Edition
                             Version 1.4.0

				CHANGES
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Thank you for downloading this upgrade release of the Java(TM) 2 
Runtime Environment.  This release contains many new features and 
enhanced functionality as compared with previous releases of the 
Java 2 Runtime Environment.  For more information, see:

   * On-line release notes.
     http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.4/relnotes.html

   * Changes in this release.
     http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.4/changes.html

   * Summary of New Features - Features added since version 1.3 
     of the Java 2 Runtime Environment.
     http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.4/docs/relnotes/features.html

   * Guide to Features - Complete list of all features.
     http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.4/docs/index.html#guide


